---
title: Ginger Beef & Pork Rice Bowl with Pickled Cucumber & Japanese Mayo
description: Add tons of flavour to your beef with a tasty sauce mixture plus loads of veggies, then fill your bowl with a bed of rice, pickled
cucumber and a sensational mayo. This is a recipe for a bowl you won't forget.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/64facd79d61a518bafd70795-84598a70.jpeg
